Package Nodes

Class LinearNode<T>

java.lang.Object
Nodes.LinearNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of element stored in this node
public class LinearNode<T> extends Object
A class that represents a node in a linked list structure. Each node holds an element of type T and a reference to the next node.
